Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How were the members of the\NSpecial Crimes Unit assembled?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're curious...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need to look into a murder from one year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.91,0:00:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how I ended up investigating the murder of Professor Odagiri...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:18.49,Default Top,,0,0,0,,We were running surveillance on someone that was in contact with Professor Odagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:17.12,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(238,228)\fs34\bord1.6\shad1.4\4c&H000000&\4a&H00&\pos(750,525)}Metro Police Public Safety Detective \N {\fs52\shad3}Kusakabe Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.59,0:00:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The man you arrested... Nishihori Kouya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:26.50,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(232,224)\fs34\bord1.6\shad1.4\4c&H000000&\4a&H00&\pos(370,490)}Ex Criminal Psychologist \N {\fs52\shad3}Nishihori Kouya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.81,Default Top,,0,0,0,,Just punished him a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what he was researching...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I increased the voltage on his little invention as high as it would go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seemed like the case was closed after Nishihori's testimony...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:44.01,Default Top,,0,0,0,,Professor Odagiri died...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:44.14,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(239,227)\fs34\bord1.6\shad1.4\4c&H000000&\4a&H00&\pos(620,480)}Shinkyo University Human Sciences Dept \N {\fs52\shad3}Kasai Hitomi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.51,0:00:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The professor's assistant, Kasai Hitomi, confessed to the same murder.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's telling the truth?\NWhich one is the real killer?{\i0}
