Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:15.59,OP,,0,0,0,,The rain stops, there's a break in the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:18.55,OP,,0,0,0,,The blue sky's calling out to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:22.93,OP,,0,0,0,,Alright, it's almost time to head out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:26.27,OP,,0,0,0,,I don't need anyone else's advice
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:29.19,OP,,0,0,0,,I've gotta trust my own instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:34.24,OP,,0,0,0,,It's high time I found my own way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:36.45,OP,,0,0,0,,Fire Up, Ignition
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:39.12,OP,,0,0,0,,The heavy pressure's on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:41.37,OP,,0,0,0,,Slam the accelerator and power through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:46.54,OP,,0,0,0,,Surprise, the whole world's got drive!\N{\fs30}(It's faster than ever)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:51.71,OP,,0,0,0,,Feeling high like you're finally awake\N{\fs30}(Show me your Drivin')
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:57.26,OP,,0,0,0,,Once you're on the road to destiny\N{\fs30}(Keep chasin' forever)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:01.93,OP,,0,0,0,,There's no way to go in reverse...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.68,OP,,0,0,0,,All we need is Drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Odagiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He... plagiarized my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He plagiarized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:31.74,Default Top,,0,0,0,,I had my computer protected with a password, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:30.67,EpTitle,,0,0,0,,{\fad(398,478)\an1\move(1189,620,350,620,23,397)\fs42}Episode 2{\c&H5B42D3&\3c&HDAE3E6&}   What{\c\3c\be1} is the Anima System?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He found a way to bypass the login through the network connection... {in other words, he accessed her files while she was using the internet.  Let's try to keep this as unspecific as possible so people don't get all A HUR DUR THAT'S NOT HOW COMPUTERS WORK.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he stole my research data...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something like that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If he was using the Anima System.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:03:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Anima System... What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It allows you to dive into the internet and move about freely...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how he described it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That research he stole was everything to me, it was my life's work...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I couldn't let him get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Professor had no signs of trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He... had a heart condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he was so busy with his research, I prepared his medicine every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:52.92,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(485,475)\4a00\fs56\shad3\bord1.6\pos(640,570)\3c&H010100&}April 8th, 2014 (Tuesday)  6:05 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:52.41,Default Top,,0,0,0,,But that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,After I found out what he'd done to my work...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I prepared a different medicine, one that would put an intense strain on his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,After he drank that water, I'm sure he...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:53.98,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(238,228)\fs30\bord1.6\shad1.4\4c&H000000&\4a00\pos(535,490)}Shinkyo University Human Sciences Dept Professor\N{\fs52\shad3}Odagiri Masahiko
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a hell of a thing you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't be sure she's the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinnosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, Tomari!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the autopsy, there were no\Nsigns of poison found in the Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that's the case, then how did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Another person has confessed to this crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishihori Kouya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I recreated Professor Odagiri's invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishihori said he turned the voltage all the way up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:05:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll do the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, time for science!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it kills me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine, trust me! Kiriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait, wait! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here comes the helmet. \N- No, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I'm begging you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon Kiriko, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can feel it...\NIt's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It kinda... tingles a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, experiment complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we know that turning up the voltage isn't lethal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the professor had a weak heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishihori couldn't have killed the professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means it wasn't Kasai or Nishihori?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that doesn't rule anyone out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishihori said something strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Professor Odagiri sounded pretty proud of himself...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the Anima System...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mankind will be free from the limitation of death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Kasai Hitomi said it, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It allows you to dive into the internet and move about freely...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how he described it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If a network connection is a clue in this case... {inter or intranet, so let's keep it ambiguous for now}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the Roidmudes may be involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Roidmudes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You said they were born on the internet, right Krim?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:07:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When Banno and I were working on the android technology...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,None of their actual development involved the internet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Banno hid a malicious artificial intelligence in the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The leaders of the androids exhibited individualistic will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They called themselves Roidmudes, and they killed Banno and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to aid them in the war on mankind, they took their malicious cores and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,created 108 Roidmudes, releasing them into the digital abyss of the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cores roamed through the network,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,absorbing human emotions and spreading all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultimately converting their code\Ninto physical form as Roidmudes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What if the Anima System really is \Nconnected to the Roidmudes, somehow...{If the Anima system is really connected to the Roidmudes...}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? You said it was important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enlighten me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your relationship with \NProfessor Odagiri, who died last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who? I never heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Well that's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talking to a student from Shinkyo University...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems that someone unaffiliated with the school was seen visiting the professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now do you wanna talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted some advice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Advice? About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The internet stuff the Professor was studying...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an SNS anime community...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What was he researching?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know! Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, not so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you lie when I first asked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kusakabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kusakabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried calling you a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get my messages?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was occupied with other matters at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Such troubling, idiotic, tedious matters...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping to ask you some more questions about Professor Odagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything would help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not dig any deeper into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider this a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Any further and someone is going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:10:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's trouble! Hurry back to headquarters!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Saijou...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's hiding something about Professor Odagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right kid, we're not gonna hurt y—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed Professor Odagiri! I did it!
