Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think someone is after my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he used to run into Banno a lot during his walks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Banno was already dead, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he have seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be Kusakabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,His attitude was completely different from when we first met...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can commit a murder without leaving any evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:36.52,Default Top,,0,0,0,,I think we might be closer to the truth than we realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:36.52,EndTitle,,0,0,0,,{\clip(m 1124 606 l 1128 600 1136 588 1144 586 1152 576 1166 570 1170 534 151 536 152 594 166 614)\shad2.4\c&H0B00E8&\3c&HF9FDF7&\move(1025,600,177,600,22,355)}Episode 3  {\c&H0B00E8&\3c&HF9FDF7&}Who{\c&HF9FDF7&\3c&H0B00E8&} killed Professor Odagiri?
